-= Kitchen =-
You've just shown up in a kitchen.

You can make out a fridge. The fridge is empty! This is the worst thing that could possibly happen, ever! You scan the room, seeing an oven. There's something strange about this being here, but you can't put your finger on it. You see a table. On the table you make out a cookbook and a knife. Now that's what I call TextWorld! Were you looking for a counter? Because look over there, it's a counter. The counter is vast. However, the counter, like an empty counter, has nothing on it. You can make out a stove. However, the stove, like an empty stove, has nothing on it. Oh! Why couldn't there just be stuff on it?

There is an open plain door leading south. There is an open sliding patio door leading west. There is an exit to the north. Don't worry, there is no door.
